### Create New Award
POST {
    {baseUrl
    }
}/awards
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {
    {authToken
    }
}

{
    "title": "Ghana Best Awards 2025",
    "description": "An award show celebrating the best in various industries.",
    "ceremony_date": "2025-12-15T18:00:00",
